column1: Cafe Ba-Ba-Reeba!////Really enjoyed my food. Lots of fresh small bites that were spot on delicious. The olives were stand outs as well as the apple sherry dates.  Got for delivery
column2: great packaging and easier to do than I was assuming.  No real misses except for the price. Absurdly expensive for the portion size. I likely wouldn't do again due to price but I had a good fresh meal.
